## Next Steps
Once deployed to Vercel:
1. Enable Speed Insights in the Vercel project dashboard (if not already enabled)
2. Verify the tracking script appears in the page's source as `/<unique-path>/script.js`
3. Monitor the Speed Insights dashboard for performance metrics after users visit the site

## Technical Notes
- The Speed Insights component automatically tracks Core Web Vitals (LCP, FID, CLS, etc.)
- It integrates seamlessly with Vercel's infrastructure for optimal performance monitoring
- The component is designed to have minimal impact on page load performance
- Data collection respects user privacy and is compliant with GDPR

